PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Consumer and Corporate Affairs of Anthony E.H. Campbell, of Gloucester, Ontario, as a member of the Standards Council of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of John Lawrence Paynter, whose term has expired.
